name: Dojo Feng Shui
additionalNotes:
With Feng Shui, Cigar Dojo has partnered with Espinosa Premium Cigars and the company’s La Zona factory to find balance and harmony with “The Dojo’s” Asian influence. This is most quickly evident with the cigar’s square format.
